      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've had stuffy ears before and they usually go away by morning. it doesn't even hurt, it's just quiet. is it really worth a trip to the emergency room just for a clogged ear? can i just try some ear drops or some warm compress to see if it clears up? i'd rather just sleep on it and see how i feel in the morning.",
